I"1<p>This is the first game I ever wrote by myself. It’s a text adventure starring
Sonic the Hedgehog.</p>

<p>It was written in Power Basic for the Atari ST. The source code is extremely
scrappy and has some wonderfully useless comments and variable names.</p>

<p>For example, the code to handle the “TALK” command looks like this:</p>

<div class="language-visualbasic highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c1">'IT'S GOOD TO TALK!</span>
